parameters: It seems to be a pedestal for placing something.
Do you want to place the crystal on the pedestal?
Mage Relm (I have a bad feeling about this...)
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mage Relm: The demon Yuan, who was defeated by the hero, may
be much stronger than the illusions we have encountered so
far.
Mage Relm: Here come the illusions!

Mage Relm's illusion: This crystal is amazing...! Who on
earth created something like this!?

Mage Relm's illusion: This strange sensation... It feels
like time and space are reversing... I have a feeling that I
can reach the truth.

Mage Relm's illusion: Next... this is... directly in my
mind... Ah... I see... I have to... go to that place...
Clea: This is different from before.
Thief Nora: There's no sign of the enemy anywhere!

Priestess Sophia: Take a good look! What's shining is an
[invitation letter]!

Mage Relm: I-I'm fine... Please look at this, the invitation
letter has changed.

Mage Relm: To the wonderful seekers, wait at the place
covered in Monimos Mountain's crystal.

Mage Relm: It seems like we have obtained the right to meet
Albus, don't we?

Priestess Sophia: I wonder if it's really Albus himself. Is
there a possibility that someone is luring us out?

Mage Relm: A human who can manipulate such powerful magic...
I don't think it's possible considering his specialization
is crystals.

Clea: We won't know unless we go and see for ourselves,
right?
Mage Relm: That's right, let's head to Monimos Mountain!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
It seems that the pedestal has lost its functionality.

events.name: QI『クリスタルの中の助手』
